This is despite the fact that I always criticize these falsehood stories that are aimed at insulting the believers of the Orthodox Church.

The calendar is something which is largely used by Eritreans. The calendar are used in different places and occasions to schedule different events such as weddings, business meetings, leisure, religious worship etc.

Some of the old calendars are famous for telling fortune stories. The reader familiar with the images in many eastern countries is probably well aware of the pictures and information that are in their calendars.
